content:
Hi,

My PSET 4 was scored a 50% because of a fileconfig error, even though it passed all the test cases with the student tester.

Can it be regraded manually?


Thanks,
Eric Zhou
subject: Fontconfig error: Cannot load default config file resulting in 50% pset autograder score

content:
Hi Eric,

The fontconfig error does not actually affect your score. However, your code did timeout on the server after 4 seconds. We will manually regrade psets that went over the 4 second limit on the server, so your pset should also be regraded.

Best,

Matt
